review_text: Really nice place where you can relax in peace. Outstanding.

(Translated by Google) Beautiful park. Water games. Basketball court. Children's corner. Shelter in case of rain. We regret, however, a space for the barbecue; we also regret that there is no pool. The trees bring a lot of freshness.

(Original)
Beau parc .Jeux d'eaux. Terrain de basket. Coin des petits. Abri en cas de pluie. On regrette toutefois un espace pour le barbecue ; on regrette egalement qu'il n'y aie pas de piscine. Les arbres apportent beaucoup de fraicheur.
